  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.280", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Noch immer gibt es davon viel zu viele in den Bilanzen diverser Banken der Euro-Zone. "
